@SpanSight.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5194

### Liveness (no dependencies) and readiness (DB reachable)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/healthz

###

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/readyz

### OpenAPI document — interactive reference at {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/scalar/v1

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### Code → label lookups (conditions, materials, designs, states)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/lookups

### National stats for the KPI strip

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/stats/summary

### Bridges — first page, no filters

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges?page=1&pageSize=10

### Bridges — combined filters (FR-0.3 AC-1): poor-condition steel in Florida, built before 1970
### (material/design take NBI item-43 codes — see /api/lookups; 3 = Steel, 4 = Steel continuous)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges?state=FL&condition=Poor&material=3&material=4&yearBuiltMax=1970

### Bridges — bounding box (minLon,minLat,maxLon,maxLat: greater Miami) + traffic floor

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges?bbox=-80.9,25.1,-80.0,26.0&minAdt=10000

### Map layer GeoJSON (the SPA fallback when no PMTiles URL is configured)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges/geojson?state=FL

### Bridge detail — raw NBI codes decoded (fixture bridge CR-905, Miami-Dade)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges/FL/1238705001

### Unknown structure → RFC 9457 404 ProblemDetails

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges/FL/DOES-NOT-EXIST

### Invalid parameters → 400 ValidationProblem with field-level detail

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/bridges?bbox=not-a-bbox&pageSize=99999

### Data-QA summary — reconciles exactly with the latest ingestion run (FR-0.2 AC-3)

GET {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/qa/summary

### AI natural-language query (FR-AI.1) — 503 until Ai:Enabled at the Phase 0.5 gate (ADR-008)

POST {{SpanSight.Api_HostAddress}}/api/ai/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "poor-condition steel bridges near Miami built before 1970"
}
